## 3. 关键入口点

### 3.1 Coredump.java (主 SDK 类)

```java
// 获取单例
Coredump coredump = Coredump.getInstance();

// 初始化
coredump.init();

// 配置 core dump 参数
coredump.setCoreDir("/storage/emulated/0/Android/data/penguin.opencore.tester/files");
coredump.setCoreFlag(Coredump.FLAG_CORE | Coredump.FLAG_PID | Coredump.FLAG_TID);
coredump.setCoreFilter(Coredump.FILTER_SPECIAL_VMA | Coredump.FILTER_SANITIZER_SHADOW_VMA);
coredump.setCoreTimeout(120);

// 启用崩溃捕获
coredump.enable(Coredump.JAVA);   // Java 崩溃
coredump.enable(Coredump.NATIVE);  // Native 崩溃

// 设置回调监听器
coredump.setListener(new Coredump.Listener() {
    @Override
    public void onCompleted(String path) {
        Log.i("Coredump", "Core saved: " + path);
    }
});

// 手动触发 core dump
coredump.doCoredump();
```

### 3.2 MainActivity.java (测试应用)

```java
public class MainActivity extends AppCompatActivity implements Coredump.Listener {

    // 触发 Java 崩溃
    private void doJavaCrash() {
        new Thread(() -> {
            View view = null;
            view.callOnClick(); // NullPointerException
        }).start();
    }

    // 触发 Native 崩溃
    private void doNativeCrash() {
        new Thread(this::nativeCrashJNI).start();
    }

    // 手动触发 core dump（不崩溃）
    private void doDirectJavaCore() {
        Coredump.getInstance().doCoredump();
    }

    @Override
    public void onCompleted(String path) {
        Log.i(Coredump.TAG, path);
        Toast.makeText(this, path, Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();
    }
}
